            . I am the wife of John Whitford - we live in Lizard-street. I saw the prisoner come to the street door, and look out - he then went in, and came out with a bundle under his right arm; I was in the room when this blanket was produced.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-88-person727">
