            . I am a Police constable. I took the prisoner, and have the sheet, which I got from another officer who brought it out of the house, and the blanket from Mrs. Storey.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-88-person728">
                  ELIZABETH 
                  ROBINSON
               <interp inst="t18310630-88-person728" type="surname" value="ROBINSON"></interp>
