                     <interp inst="t18310630-88-person728" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . These are my property, I believe, but I cannot swear to them - I am out a great deal, and my house is left in the care of a child; here is an R on the sheet, and some of my things are so marked.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I believe the prosecutrix is well aware that it was not my intention to steal them; she has called on my friends, and stated that she would not have thought of prosecuting me but for the Policeman.</p>
